        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p> <bold><b>Saving Local News Act</b></bold> </p> <p>This bill includes as a tax-exempt 501(c)(3) charitable organization purpose the publication (including electronic publication) of written news articles.</p> <p>In the case of an organization that is tax-exempt due to the publication of written news articles, the term <i>unrelated business taxable incom</i>e does not include any amount attributable to payments for advertisements in news publications.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
